claim.claim-text:
1. A device for covering openings having a frame in buildings comprising: 
a covering coupled to the frame; 
at least one hinge for coupling said door to said frame; 
at least one rotatable handle, rotatably coupled to said door; 
at least one rotatable shaft coupled to said rotatable handle; and 
at least one stationary shaft coupled to said rotatable shaft, wherein when said door rotates within the door frame, said at least one rotatable shaft rotates around said at least one stationary shaft causing said at least one rotatable handle to rotate as said door is rotating.

14. A device for covering openings having a frame in buildings comprising: 
a covering coupled to the frame; 
at least one hinge for coupling said door to said frame; 
at least one rotatable handle, rotatably coupled to said door; 
at least one rotatable shaft coupled to said rotatable handle; and 
at least one stationary shaft coupled to said rotatable shaft; 
a drive means for coupling said at least one stationary shaft and said at least one rotatable shaft together wherein when said door rotates within the door frame, said at least one rotatable shaft rotates around said at least one stationary shaft using said drive means and causing said at least one rotatable handle to rotate as said door is rotating.

15. A door disposed in a door frame the door having a drive device comprising: 
at least one rotatable handle rotatably coupled to said door; 
at least one rotatable shaft coupled fast to said handle and rotatably coupled to said door; 
at least one additional rotatable shaft rotatably coupled to said door; 
at least one stationary shaft coupled to the frame; and 
a series of bevel gears with at least one bevel gear attached to each of said rotatable shaft, said additional rotatable shaft and said stationary shaft, so that when a user opens or closes said door, said additional rotatable shaft rotates about said at least one stationary shaft, and said rotatable shaft rotates with said additional rotatable shaft so that said handle rotates as the door rotates.
